{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 12,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 309.327,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.718,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then the angel said to me:",
      "verse": "12:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 1.898,
      "end": 3.756,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look, and behold your seed,",
      "verse": "12:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 3.936,
      "end": 6.212,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also the seed of your brothers.",
      "verse": "12:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 6.392,
      "end": 8.993,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked and saw the land of promise;",
      "verse": "12:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 9.173,
      "end": 11.356,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw multitudes of people,",
      "verse": "12:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 11.536,
      "end": 16.366,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "indeed, even as it were in number as many as the sand of the sea.",
      "verse": "12:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 17.046,
      "end": 18.857,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw multitudes",
      "verse": "12:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 19.037,
      "end": 21.034,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "gathered together to battle,",
      "verse": "12:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 21.214,
      "end": 22.561,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "one against the other;",
      "verse": "12:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 22.741,
      "end": 24.227,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw wars,",
      "verse": "12:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 24.407,
      "end": 26.079,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and rumors of wars,",
      "verse": "12:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 26.259,
      "end": 29.649,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and great slaughters with the sword among my people.",
      "verse": "12:2",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 30.329,
      "end": 33.208,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw many generations pass away,",
      "verse": "12:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 33.388,
      "end": 36.964,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after the manner of wars and contentions in the land;",
      "verse": "12:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 37.144,
      "end": 38.909,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw many cities,",
      "verse": "12:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 39.089,
      "end": 41.597,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "indeed, even that I did not number them.",
      "verse": "12:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 42.277,
      "end": 45.017,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw a mist of darkness",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 45.197,
      "end": 47.658,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "on the face of the land of promise;",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 47.838,
      "end": 49.417,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw lightnings,",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 49.597,
      "end": 54.102,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I heard thunderings, and earthquakes, and all manner of tumultuous noises;",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 54.282,
      "end": 57.347,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw the earth and the rocks, that they rent;",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 57.527,
      "end": 60.406,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw mountains tumbling into pieces;",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 60.586,
      "end": 63.047,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw the plains of the earth,",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 63.227,
      "end": 64.806,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they were broken up;",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 64.986,
      "end": 67.912,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw many cities that they were sunk;",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 68.092,
      "end": 71.203,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw many that they were burned with fire;",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 71.383,
      "end": 73.844,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw many that tumbled to the earth,",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 74.024,
      "end": 75.835,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the quaking of it.",
      "verse": "12:4",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 76.515,
      "end": 78.651,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then after I saw these things,",
      "verse": "12:5",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 78.831,
      "end": 81.014,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I saw the vapor of darkness,",
      "verse": "12:5",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 81.194,
      "end": 83.702,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it passed from off the face of the earth;",
      "verse": "12:5",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 83.882,
      "end": 87.086,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and behold, I saw multitudes who had not fallen",
      "verse": "12:5",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 87.266,
      "end": 91.028,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the great and terrible judgments of the Lord.",
      "verse": "12:5",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 91.708,
      "end": 93.519,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw the heavens open,",
      "verse": "12:6",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 93.699,
      "end": 96.578,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Lamb of God descending out of heaven;",
      "verse": "12:6",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 96.758,
      "end": 98.941,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he came down and showed himself to them.",
      "verse": "12:6",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 99.621,
      "end": 101.711,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I also saw and bear record",
      "verse": "12:7",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 101.891,
      "end": 104.956,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Holy Ghost fell upon twelve others;",
      "verse": "12:7",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 105.136,
      "end": 107.737,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were ordained of God, and chosen.",
      "verse": "12:7",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 108.417,
      "end": 110.414,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel spoke to me, saying:",
      "verse": "12:8",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 110.594,
      "end": 113.148,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold the twelve disciples of the Lamb,",
      "verse": "12:8",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 113.328,
      "end": 115.836,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who are chosen to minister to your seed.",
      "verse": "12:8",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 116.516,
      "end": 117.909,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said to me:",
      "verse": "12:9",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 118.089,
      "end": 120.829,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "You rememberest the twelve apostles of the Lamb?",
      "verse": "12:9",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 121.009,
      "end": 122.495,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold they are they",
      "verse": "12:9",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 122.675,
      "end": 125.461,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who shall judge the twelve tribes of Israel;",
      "verse": "12:9",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 125.641,
      "end": 129.681,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, the twelve ministers of your seed shall be judged of them;",
      "verse": "12:9",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 129.861,
      "end": 132.555,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for you are of the house of Israel.",
      "verse": "12:9",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 133.235,
      "end": 137.693,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And these twelve ministers whom you behold shall judge your seed.",
      "verse": "12:10",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 137.873,
      "end": 140.288,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And, behold, they are righteous forever;",
      "verse": "12:10",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 140.468,
      "end": 143.301,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for because of their faith in the Lamb of God",
      "verse": "12:10",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 143.481,
      "end": 145.989,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "their garments are made white in his blood.",
      "verse": "12:10",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 146.669,
      "end": 148.294,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel said to me:",
      "verse": "12:11",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 148.474,
      "end": 149.31,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Look!",
      "verse": "12:11",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 149.49,
      "end": 153.484,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked, and saw three generations pass away in righteousness;",
      "verse": "12:11",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 153.664,
      "end": 155.661,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their garments were white",
      "verse": "12:11",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 155.841,
      "end": 157.652,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even like to the Lamb of God.",
      "verse": "12:11",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 157.832,
      "end": 159.457,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel said to me:",
      "verse": "12:11",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 159.637,
      "end": 162.284,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "These are made white in the blood of the Lamb,",
      "verse": "12:11",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 162.464,
      "end": 164.693,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of their faith in him.",
      "verse": "12:11",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 165.373,
      "end": 168.81,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, also saw many of the fourth generation",
      "verse": "12:12",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 168.99,
      "end": 171.312,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who passed away in righteousness.",
      "verse": "12:12",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 171.992,
      "end": 175.939,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw the multitudes of the earth gathered together.",
      "verse": "12:13",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 176.619,
      "end": 178.244,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel said to me:",
      "verse": "12:14",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 178.424,
      "end": 181.489,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold your seed, and also the seed of your brothers.",
      "verse": "12:14",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 182.169,
      "end": 184.259,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I looked",
      "verse": "12:15",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 184.439,
      "end": 186.482,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and saw the people of my seed",
      "verse": "12:15",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 186.662,
      "end": 188.984,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "gathered together in multitudes",
      "verse": "12:15",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 189.164,
      "end": 191.672,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "against the seed of my brothers;",
      "verse": "12:15",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 191.852,
      "end": 194.128,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were gathered together to battle.",
      "verse": "12:15",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 194.808,
      "end": 196.805,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel spoke to me, saying:",
      "verse": "12:16",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 196.985,
      "end": 200.514,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold the fountain of filthy water which your father saw;",
      "verse": "12:16",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 200.694,
      "end": 203.295,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "indeed, even the river of which he spoke;",
      "verse": "12:16",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 203.475,
      "end": 206.122,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the depths of it are the depths of hell.",
      "verse": "12:16",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 206.802,
      "end": 208.845,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the mists of darkness",
      "verse": "12:17",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 209.025,
      "end": 211.208,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "are the temptations of the devil,",
      "verse": "12:17",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 211.388,
      "end": 212.874,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which blinds the eyes,",
      "verse": "12:17",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 213.054,
      "end": 215.84,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and hardens the hearts of the children of men,",
      "verse": "12:17",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 216.02,
      "end": 218.714,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and leads them away into broad roads,",
      "verse": "12:17",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 218.894,
      "end": 221.17,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they perish and are lost.",
      "verse": "12:17",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 221.85,
      "end": 224.265,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the large and spacious building,",
      "verse": "12:18",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 224.445,
      "end": 227.556,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which your father saw, is vain imaginations",
      "verse": "12:18",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 227.736,
      "end": 229.919,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the pride of the children of men.",
      "verse": "12:18",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 230.099,
      "end": 233.35,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And a great and a terrible gulf divides them;",
      "verse": "12:18",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 233.53,
      "end": 236.92,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "indeed, even the word of the justice of the Eternal God,",
      "verse": "12:18",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 237.1,
      "end": 239.654,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Messiah who is the Lamb of God,",
      "verse": "12:18",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 239.834,
      "end": 242.249,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of whom the Holy Ghost bears record,",
      "verse": "12:18",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 242.429,
      "end": 246.237,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the beginning of the world until this time,",
      "verse": "12:18",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 246.417,
      "end": 249.064,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and from this time henceforth and forever.",
      "verse": "12:18",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 249.744,
      "end": 251.88,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And while the angel spoke these words,",
      "verse": "12:19",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 252.06,
      "end": 253.082,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I saw and saw",
      "verse": "12:19",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 253.262,
      "end": 256.652,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the seed of my brothers contended against my seed,",
      "verse": "12:19",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 256.832,
      "end": 259.293,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the word of the angel;",
      "verse": "12:19",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 259.473,
      "end": 261.795,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and because of the pride of my seed,",
      "verse": "12:19",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 261.975,
      "end": 263.972,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the temptations of the devil,",
      "verse": "12:19",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 264.152,
      "end": 268.332,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I saw that the seed of my brothers overpowered the people of my seed.",
      "verse": "12:19",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 269.012,
      "end": 270.452,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw,",
      "verse": "12:20",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 270.632,
      "end": 273.836,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and saw the people of the seed of my brothers",
      "verse": "12:20",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 274.016,
      "end": 276.152,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they had overcome my seed;",
      "verse": "12:20",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 276.332,
      "end": 279.815,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they went forth in multitudes upon the face of the land.",
      "verse": "12:20",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 280.495,
      "end": 283.885,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw them gathered together in multitudes;",
      "verse": "12:21",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 284.065,
      "end": 287.316,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw wars and rumors of wars among them;",
      "verse": "12:21",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 287.496,
      "end": 291.768,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and in wars and rumors of wars I saw many generations pass away.",
      "verse": "12:21",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 292.448,
      "end": 294.073,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the angel said to me:",
      "verse": "12:22",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 294.253,
      "end": 296.668,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold these shall dwindle in unbelief.",
      "verse": "12:22",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 297.348,
      "end": 298.788,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I saw,",
      "verse": "12:23",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 298.968,
      "end": 301.29,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after they had dwindled in unbelief",
      "verse": "12:23",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 301.47,
      "end": 305.046,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they became a dark, and loathsome, and a filthy people,",
      "verse": "12:23",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 305.226,
      "end": 308.663,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "full of idleness and all manner of wicked practices.",
      "verse": "12:23",
      "lineIndex": 111
    }
  ]
}